description:
The New Balance 9060 Triple Black exemplifies the essence of simplicity and versatility in a sports shoe.

Constructed with a breathable mesh and soft suede upper, the Triple Black New Balance 9060 prioritizes both comfort and temperature regulation, preventing overheating. Predominantly black, the mesh upper introduces a slightly softer dark charcoal hue, creating a balanced contrast. The iconic midfoot "N" motifs seamlessly integrate with the understated sole units, contributing to a unified aesthetic. The tongue logo pays homage to the original 991 lace jewel. Underneath, the sculpted pod midsole incorporates ABZORB, ENCAP, and SBS cushioning for optimal comfort.

The most noteworthy feature of the New Balance 9060 Triple Black is its sculpted pod midsole, which includes ABZORB, ENCAP, and SBS cushioning. This aspect ensures enduring comfort, establishing the shoe as an excellent choice for everyday wear. The sneaker was originally sold for $150 on September 22nd, 2023.

The New Balance 9060 Black Castlerock Grey was inspired by a 90s model and comes in a grey, black, and red colorway.

This Black New Balance 9060 sneaker consists of a black mesh base with monochromatic pigskin suede and leather overlays. The shoe is designed with "N" branding on the side panel, a plush tongue, and flat laces. The model has a CR device at the heel. The design is completed by a chunky, dual-density midsole equipped with ABZORB and SBS cushioning.

The New Balance 9060 Black Castlerock Grey was released on September 2nd, 2022, at a retail price of $150.

description:
The New Balance 9060 Rain Cloud Grey takes on an early 2000s design by the American brand.

The sneaker displays tones of grey and off-white. It features a mixed-material upper that combines pigskin suede overlays with mesh, and the "N" emblem is accented with multiple silver details. The medial logo has a deconstructed appearance made up of parallel lines, while the"N" is solid on the lateral. The dual-density midsole, which sits on top of the diamond-shaped outsole, combines SBS cushioning and ABZORB technology.

The New Balance 9060 Rain Cloud Grey debuted on September 2nd, 2022, and originally retailed at $150.

The New Balance 530 White Silver Navy features a white mesh upper with metallic silver and white leather overlays. On the quarter panel, a grey New Balance logo outlined in navy adds contrast. From there, a white and grey ABZORB sole adds the finishing touch.

The New Balance 530 White Silver Navy released in February of 2021 and retailed for $95.

The New Balance 9060 Black Cement is a sleek and stylish addition to the popular 9060 line. This men's sneaker features a predominantly black colorway with subtle cement accents, creating a versatile and sophisticated look. The upper is crafted with a combination of premium materials, including mesh and suede overlays, providing both durability and breathability. The shoe's chunky sole unit incorporates New Balance's innovative cushioning technology, ensuring superior comfort and support for all-day wear.

Designed with both fashion and function in mind, the 9060 Black Cement boasts a modern silhouette that pays homage to New Balance's heritage while embracing contemporary aesthetics. The shoe's distinctive design elements, such as the exaggerated heel and sculpted midsole, offer a unique visual appeal that sets it apart from other sneakers in its class. With its blend of style, comfort, and quality craftsmanship, the New Balance 9060 Black Cement is an excellent choice for sneaker enthusiasts and casual wearers alike. Our experts state this product is great for those seeking a versatile, comfortable sneaker that effortlessly transitions from casual outings to more dressed-up occasions.

description:
The New Balance 1906R White Metallic Gold comes in a metallic silver and metallic gold color scheme.

The New Balance 1906R White Metallic Gold adopts a classic silhouette with white leather and gold embellishments. The upper is breathable and lightweight, with a cushioned collar and tongue for comfort. The midsole is constructed from lightweight EVA foam for cushioning and support. Durable rubber is used to construct the outsole, which provides grip and steadiness. The shoe also features "N" branding in a contrasting gold and black colorway on both lateral sides.

The New Balance 1906R White Metallic Gold was made available on August 12th, 2022, for a retail price of $155.

description: The New Balance 9060 Sea Salt White is a sleek and stylish sneaker that combines modern design with classic elements. The upper is made of premium leather and mesh, providing durability and breathability. The sea salt white colorway gives the shoe a clean and minimalist look, making it a versatile addition to any wardrobe. The release date for this shoe is January 14th, 2023, and with a retail price of $150. The New Balance 9060 Sea Salt White is perfect for those who want a comfortable and fashionable sneaker that can be worn for any occasion. With its high-quality materials and attention to detail, this shoe is sure to impress.

description:
The New Balance 1906L Metallic Silver reimagines the 1906 as a slip-on loafer. This hybrid sneaker showcases a futuristic color palette of metallic silver and grey.

Seamlessly blending New Balance‚Äôs technical specs with the design requirements of a loafer, the Metallic Silver New Balance 1906L is lace-free. With N-ergy cushioning underfoot for shock absorption, the sneaker offers long-lasting comfort. The upper is crafted from a loose weave mesh that ensures durability, while the metallic silver accents draw attention to the supportive overlays. Although the sneaker doesn‚Äôt need laces, a traditional loafer apron crosses the tongue. It features a silver metallic sheen that matches the collar.

While many loafers include a tassel hanging over the vamp, this version doesn‚Äôt include a tassel. Our experts appreciate this exclusion because it maintains the sneaker‚Äôs sporty aesthetic. The New Balance 1906L Metallic Silver was released on September 19, 2024, and sold for $150.

description:
The New Balance 9060 Triple White takes the classic 9060 silhouette and adds an all-white colorway. Including white on the upper, outsole, midsole, and lining allows the sneaker‚Äôs design elements to stand out.

This version of the 9060 finds inspiration in the 990 and the 860, giving the lifestyle shoe an early 2000s aesthetic. It features wavy leather overlays on the upper that complement the wavy pattern on the thick midsole. The upper is made of breathable mesh, while the heel displays a transparent CR device. This feature can be found on other 9060 models and supports heel stability. Although the curving logo on the tongue resembles the lace jewel on the 991, the diamond-like pattern of the outsole finds inspiration in the 860.

Our StockX experts like how ABZORB cushioning and pods in the midsole contribute to the sneaker‚Äôs chunky appearance. The New Balance 9060 Triple White was released on January 12th, 2024, and retailed at $150.

The New Balance 9060 Triple Black Leather applies a black-on-black colorway and premium materials to the 9060‚Äôs technical silhouette.

This New Balance 9060 combines elements from two high-performance predecessors ‚Äì the 990 and the 860. While several technical features are borrowed from the 990, the sneaker‚Äôs style details come from the 860. The upper features black mesh with soft suede and synthetic leather overlays. The incorporation of mesh allows the foot to breathe and reduces the shoe‚Äôs overall weight. The overlays create a wavy pattern that complements the curves of the chunky midsole and rubber outsole. The signature New Balance ‚ÄòN‚Äô can be found on the side panels in tonal black leather.

Our StockX experts like the addition of a stacked ABZORB midsole, which gives the shoe a semi-bulky appearance and reduces impact stress. The New Balance 9060 Triple Black Leather was released on September 24th, 2023, and retailed at $170.

The New Balance 9060 Bone Sparrow shoe, presenting in a natural inspired color scheme of bone and sparrow, boasts a chunky and bold silhouette and is designed for casual wear and light athletic activity.

When the New Balance 9060 was being designed, it sparked a new word: retrofuturism. And the evidence of that word is present in this low-top shoe that is packed with New Balance‚Äôs sneaker tech while ebbing and flowing "retro" and "futurism" styles. The primarily bone colored upper is made out of suede, mesh, and synthetic materials which all work together to ensure it looks and feels great. Two different tilted Ns, sporting sparrow colored accents, adorn the sides, while additional branding is on the heel and tongue.

We particularly like sneaker tech designed with comfort in mind, such as the brand‚Äôs ABZORB midsole, ABZORB SBS heel, and the translucent CR device on the heel. The New Balance 9060 Bone Sparrow retailed for $150 when it was released on October 28, 2024.
